headline: Transdigm Group Incorporated Announces Cessation of Jessica L. Warren as General Counsel, Chief Compliance Officer, and Secretary
summary: Effective July 7, 2025, Jessica L. Warren ceased serving as General Counsel, Chief Compliance Officer, and Secretary of TransDigm Group Incorporated ....
